# Secrets — never copy env files into image layers
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env*.example

# Dependencies & logs (npm ci reinstalls inside the image; logs are noise)
**/node_modules
*.log

# Build caches / outputs not needed in the build context
**/.expo
apps/backend/dist
apps/backend/storage
apps/mobile/ios/Pods
apps/mobile/ios/build
apps/mobile/android/.gradle
apps/mobile/android/build
apps/mobile/android/app/build

# Test / CI / editor artifacts
e2e/.auth
e2e/playwright-report
e2e/test-results
test-results
playwright-report
coverage
.vscode
.claude
**/.DS_Store
